g":"其實佩恩篇後最錯既決定就係冇開第三部<br />\n如果佩恩篇後用五影會談篇做結尾,鳴佐條橋打番幾集之後再修練一兩年<br />\n用番呢個模式可能會好好多<br />\n<br />\n一黎鳴人同佐助都其實真係有野要練,一個要去學尾獸,一個要開永恆眼<br />\n可以打忍戰,但最大問題係忍戰前期雜亂無章<br />\n岸本完全唔識寫戰爭,只係將十場戰鬥擺埋一齊講<br />\n去到忍戰中後期先好睇番<br />\n<br />\n至於斑有震攝力定PAIN有震攝力D,其實兩個人物唔同<br />\n斑都係一直有鋪排,話係忍界最強咁濟,算係神話級人物<br />\nPAIN就係當時既當代最強<br />\n帶土就可以行埋一二面,一開始話佢係鳴人相反,但鳴人貫徹自己既大愛,帶土冇貫徹自己既邪惡,已經完全唔同級"},{"pid":"b3f6b80b6df441d97c991a8ef50f7cf43cfb562c","tid":130763,"uid":82889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T19:11:50.000Z","msg":"個人覺得話係少年漫既頂峰其實都冇錯<br />\n隔離兩個巨頭都冇一個章節拍得上呢章<br />\n我比你計埋龍珠,龍珠角色除左柒達外根本無火影果D咁有故事,唔會交代到一個現代人睇完都有所反省既MSG"},{"pid":"bf4e3f584f94ab9ce16e909318716d38856383e3","tid":130763,"uid":2784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T05:47:29.000Z","msg":"火影世界第一"},{"pid":"9f0adc7237d19a1489e6f33c86b8be1953202f6c","tid":130763,"uid":31925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T06:00:11.000Z","msg":"我就係睇到地圖炮滅木葉之後<br />\n即刻棄左唔撚睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n忍者故事話知你變咩我都接受到<br />\n地圖炮打全場係撚忍術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成個故事去到六道呢個位開始完全失衡<br />\n咩咩老師上忍全部變哂路人咁滯<br />\n啲設定仲衰撚過大陸啲修真小說<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"372d1d99ae6002c2eb01b2adfeccd853505d766a","tid":130763,"uid":34872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T06:00:19.000Z","msg":"宇智波條線重重複複咁講 悶到傻<br />\n帶土假死都唔知loop左幾多次+每次講大道理<br />\n佩恩一開始著眼點係淪迴眼 比到人新鮮既感覺<br />\n比寫輪眼更加強 個對比出左黎"},{"pid":"f8a5121304f57e1951023719e6609d4842379490","tid":130763,"uid":17761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T06:11:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UMwwi8blCRs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DUMwwi8blCRs&d=mly3UyGsD7RWnvW57yDWjhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=94f35463\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UMwwi8blCRs</a><br />\n呢段木葉丸好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> bgm既運用 老師由一個仆街變真男人<br />\n木葉丸用螺旋丸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢到真係好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebb8f047b02b2d7fd92658a92253ddd2e51cbca3","tid":130763,"uid":54617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T06:17:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/large/14a200068ac20765475f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2Flarge%2F14a200068ac20765475f&h=3a29a595&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但我的痛楚在你之上</blockquote><br />\n樓上岩岩先有人話動畫屌打漫畫<br />\n人唔笑狗都吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e947510cc833dd4bb245707926dab8a85fc18b22","tid":130763,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T09:51:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">亮你老母點</span></span>"},{"pid":"8ab47ae81a98264c29c6c8cf4a8f7b6d5320d4b9","tid":130763,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T09:52:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">亮你老母點</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">亮你老母點</span></span><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">亮你老母點</span></span><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">亮你老母點</span></span><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">亮你老母點</span></span><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">亮你老母點</span></span><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">亮你老母點</span></span><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">亮你老母點</span></span><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">亮你老母點</span></span><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">亮你老母點</span></span><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">亮你老母點</span></span><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">亮你老母點</span></span>"},{"pid":"713a22a44f53d064479b0123afa4c2b7e0a0ee5e","tid":130763,"uid":30673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T10:09:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/large/14a200068ac20765475f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2Flarge%2F14a200068ac20765475f&h=3a29a595&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但我的痛楚在你之上</blockquote><br />\n樓上岩岩先有人話動畫屌打漫畫<br />\n人唔笑狗都吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係屌打<br />\n漫畫得初段用戰術係ok<br />\n到雛田救人 爆9尾 4代出場呢幾幕<br />\n漫畫係完全冇feel加格數完全不足<br />\n動畫有bgm本身已經激昂好多 打鬥場面都補充左唔小<br />\n雛田唔係講完一句就比人秒 係臨死都算跌斷多枝黑棒<br />\n9尾就更加唔洗講 漫畫突然就變左包骨尾獸化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 動畫係慢慢變 打到一半先解封 之後加插足夠嘅打鬥 成程係睇得好爽<br />\n到4代出場之前成個感覺係堆到上高潮 一出果下係估唔到+放鬆哂<br />\n<br />\npain果幾張臉容扭曲係製作組想表達雙方情緒激昂先咁搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小小野打哂成章精量製作"},{"pid":"e9205e452f2ead44e69470683344038e10bc8926","tid":130763,"uid":30673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T10:17:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我就係睇到地圖炮滅木葉之後<br />\n即刻棄左唔撚睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n忍者故事話知你變咩我都接受到<br />\n地圖炮打全場係撚忍術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成個故事去到六道呢個位開始完全失衡<br />\n咩咩老師上忍全部變哂路人咁滯<br />\n啲設定仲衰撚過大陸啲修真小說<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n由呢章開始入不歸路係真<br />\n但係由忍者作品變超能力作 就係疾風傳開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n至於老師變路人 其實曉d人好多都同影級交到手<br />\n殺過風火影 控制水影 活捉人柱力 殺阿c瑪<br />\n面對名義上係曉boss嘅pain<br />\n綱手都企左係到 上忍老師無發揮唔出奇<br />\n當時卡卡西已經算最top 但遇著天道+要救人<br />\n凱班就出左村"},{"pid":"a27635fe29fca6cf3fbc3c997f335fd020e726de","tid":130763,"uid":36493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T10:19:17.000Z","msg":"火影世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2075bd4ee3b01ac4c265caf42c90e20a8504ec2c","tid":130763,"uid":82889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T10:19:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我就係睇到地圖炮滅木葉之後<br />\n即刻棄左唔撚睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n忍者故事話知你變咩我都接受到<br />\n地圖炮打全場係撚忍術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成個故事去到六道呢個位開始完全失衡<br />\n咩咩老師上忍全部變哂路人咁滯<br />\n啲設定仲衰撚過大陸啲修真小說<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大家睇既野唔同<br />\nPAIN篇既MSG同埋劇情鋪排,仲有對過往伏筆既運用EG木葉丸都好神<br />\n而你只係執著係個實力設定到<br />\n老實講王道動漫係咁架啦,咩係唔係忍術姐,現實有忍者拎住個藍色波打人架咩?<br />\n忍者可以控住D雷電劈鳩人又好合理,開個巨人出黎擋又接受到,但炸爆條村就接受唔到<br />\n<br />\n同埋雖然去到後期雖然D招數升左幾個次元,但都仲係有鬥智位,鳴人同卡卡西破帶土面具果場就係好例子<br />\n最尾打斑亦都有用過謀略,只係D招式勁左好幾倍姐"},{"pid":"645b49feebd5482552bc3ed1379ccc254aca714d","tid":130763,"uid":22888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T11:28:28.000Z","msg":"火影上左神枱好耐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0dfda0d34484308493c6cbacdd8c63491576615","tid":130763,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T15:27:46.000Z","msg":"根本最難睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n完場奇怪，主角講兩句，引返長門以前講過既野就嘴遁完畢，根本完全冇解答問題。然後長門就突然變心，仲無啦啦救返晒D人<br />\n<br />\n戰力通膨嚴重，本身六隻僵屍能力已經唔多吸引（作者明顯技窮）。無啦啦搵個細路都打得死一隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，當年仲吹到螺旋丸好撚難學又好少人學到又未完成又剩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有寫輪眼設定失控，變超能力大戰，一個強國村變到屎咁廢等等，數都數唔晒<br />\n<br />\n得罪講句，睇多D漫畫先好出黎自HIGH啦"},{"pid":"12b06e5aa9e72529d5b498c401e5c585d1318bc1","tid":130763,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T15:32:36.000Z","msg":"成篇根本悶到PK<br />\n打黎打去都唔知做乜鳩<br />\n主旨兩三句，總之就係發動能力打打打，呢招好勁，我呢招仲勁咁，最後又係靠隻九尾贏<br />\n仙術系統又搞到D設定亂晒<br />\n都唔知有乜好睇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"192edf37811775d1e9e83dc59c3f9cf3453f294a","tid":130763,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T15:47:00.000Z","msg":"成套嘢最精彩係中忍考試<br />\n<br />\n忍<br />\n李洛克嘅執著、忍耐<br />\n表裡蓮華不敵<br />\n暗襯我愛羅嘅恐怖暴戾<br />\n<br />\n智<br />\n鹿丸超智遊戲<br />\n反映查克拉（術）以外的出路<br />\n探討忍者嘅本質<br />\n<br />\n勇<br />\n日向家不幸（命運）<br />\n雛田弱者嘅反抗<br />\n鳴門對決寧次<br />\n打破宿命論<br />\n<br />\n仁<br />\n鳴仁不惜用命感化我愛羅（跨國外交）<br />\n口遁化解日向家紛爭<br />\n<br />\n相反之後變成以技壓人<br />\n戰鬥力值大嘅無敵 一拳超人<br />\n鬥智變到唔重要<br />\n最搞笑係命運之子<br />\n變返宿命論 推翻前設"},{"pid":"e06bdef166af8e93fcf70e47be0fea43ab981c26","tid":130763,"uid":82889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T16:11:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成篇根本悶到PK<br />\n打黎打去都唔知做乜鳩<br />\n主旨兩三句，總之就係發動能力打打打，呢招好勁，我呢招仲勁咁，最後又係靠隻九尾贏<br />\n仙術系統又搞到D設定亂晒<br />\n都唔知有乜好睇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj